ir users, an integral element of their success. Adii discusses what  WooThemes is up to, what they’ve <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://wordpress.org/development/2010/02/menus-merge-patch-sprint/">contributed  to the WordPress</a> community and how WooThemes innovates in addressing user  problems.</p><p>In the News:</p><ul><li><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://central.wordcamp.org/">Upcoming  WordCamps</a></li><li><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://wordpress.tv/2010/07/01/introducing-vaultpress/">VaultPress  Launches</a></li><li><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://buddypress.org/2010/07/buddypress-1-2-5-2/">Another BuddyPress  Update</a></li><li><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://ocaoimh.ie/wordpress-mu-domain-mapping/">WordPress MU Domain  Mapping Update</a></li><li><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://foolswisdom.com/ab-testing-shrimptest-starts/">Conversion Rate  Optimization with ShrimpTest A/B Testing</a></li></ul><p>Plugin Picks of the Week:</p><ul><li><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/redirection/">Redirection</a></li><li><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://vaultpress.com/signup/">VaultPress</a></li><li><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/expire-password/">PassExpire</a></li></ul><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/joostdevalk/~4/APqdmzz5XdE" height="1" width="1"/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:2:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:79:"http://wp-community.org/2010/07/07/adii-pienaar-solving-problems-woothemes-way/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:17:"origEnclosureLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:133:"http://media.blubrry.com/wordpresspodcast/media.rawvoice.com/seorockstars/www2.webmasterradio.fm/mp3/wordpr