e 16 experts total, and only 18 attendees. That is what we call attention for our attendees! Now some of you might want to come, but... You can''t buy tickets just yet...</p><p><a rel="nofollow"\n target="_blank" href="http://yoast.com/seoktoberfest-2010/">SEOktoberfest 2010: looking forward to it</a> is a post from <a rel="nofollow"\n target="_blank" href="http://yoast.com/about-me/">Joost de Valk</a>''s <a rel="nofollow"\n target="_blank" href="http://yoast.com">Yoast - Tweaking Websites</a>.A good WordPress blog needs good hosting, you don''t want your blog to be slow, or, even worse, down, do you? Check out my thoughts on <a rel="nofollow"\n target="_blank" href="http://yoast.com/wordpress-hosting/">WordPress hosting</a>!</p><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/joostdevalk/~4/oE7FH92Q3XM" height="1" width="1"/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:29:"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/";a:1:{s:7:"content";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:62:"\n            \n            \n            \n            \n         ";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:2:{s:8:"duration";s:2:"90";s:6:"medium";s:5:"video";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:29:"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/";a:4:{s:6:"player";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:3:"url";s:51:"http://www.vimeo.com/moogaloop.swf?clip_id=12478333";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:69:"SEOktoberfest 2010: looking forward to it - Yoast - Tweaking Websites";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:139:"The best SEO conference out there: SEOktoberfest, in Munich, this year in September from the 21st till the 23rd. Check out the intro video!";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s: