(1512, 0, '2011-01-22 00:00:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'I began my journey into the world of nursing on an Oncology unit. I was struck by the number of women of childbearing age who would never know that joy due to numerous treatments and surgeries. The painting took on an entirely new meaning for me personally after the very complicated delivery of my own child which ultimately was the last delivery I would ever experience. While the painting embodies the darkness and emptiness of infertility it also portrays the beauty and strength of the women who endure it.', 'Gwendolyn Shafer - Ad Vitam - 2008', '', 'pending', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2011-01-22 00:00:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0, 'http://rawwar.org/?p=1512', 0, 'post', '', 0),
