(147, 3, '2010-04-19 15:04:51', '2010-04-19 22:04:51', 'CAFKA.TV was there when the Elizabeth A. Sackler Center for Feminist Art officially opened at the Brooklyn Museum.  We spoke with Martha Wilson, performance artist and Founding Director of Franklin Furnace.  Find out why she objects to the Elizabeth A. Sackler Center for Feminist Art, and how Judy Chicago made her cry.\n\nWatch for still more footage from the opening coming soon.\n\nwww.marthawilson.com\nwww.franklinfurnace.org\nwww.brooklynmuseum.org', 'Martha Wilson at the Brooklyn Museum', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'martha-wilson-at-the-brooklyn-museum', '', '', '2010-08-16 18:23:10', '2010-08-17 01:23:10', '', 0, 'http://www.rawwar.org/2010/04/martha-wilson-at-the-brooklyn-museum/', 0, 'video', '', 0),
