(878, 1, '2011-01-16 22:23:55', '2011-01-16 22:23:55', 'Carol Shield''s The Stone Diaries won the Pulitzer Prize and was short-listed for the Booker Prize. Larry''s Party won the Orange Prize. Her last novel Unless was published to critical acclaim in May 2002.\r\n\r\nThree years previously she discovered she had stage-three breast cancer. Two days after diagnosis she underwent a mastectomy and then a six-month course of radiotherapy and chemotherapy.\r\n\r\nGiven exclusive access over a period of a year, this film provides an intimate look at this gentle unassuming writer, before she lost her battle with cancer on July 16th 2003.\r\n', 'Carol Shields – Dressing Up For The Carnival: A Portrait Of Carol Shields – 2003', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'carol-shields-%e2%80%93-dressing-up-for-the-carnival-a-portrait-of-carol-shields-%e2%80%93-2003', '', '', '2011-01-17 01:07:47', '2011-01-17 01:07:47', '', 0, 'http://184.106.93.224/?p=878', 0, 'post', '', 0),
