(1051, 1, '2011-01-12 21:02:17', '2011-01-12 21:02:17', 'www.onidance.org\r\n\r\nSaliendo (USA, 2006) \r\n\r\nA film by Oni Dance and True Pictures\r\nDirectors: Maria Gillespie, Kristy Tully\r\n\r\nChoreographer: Maria Gillespie\r\n\r\nDirector of Photography: Kristy Tully\r\n\r\nEditor: Robbie Shaw\r\n\r\nMusic: Ginormous\r\n\r\nThe movement language of this work winds its way through the physical and psychological mechanics of leaving. Saliendo (translated as leaving) is part memory, part dream-state; part prophecy; all tumbling together in a kinetic passage through moments of separation. It encapsulates the tranquility and catalytic nature of attachment and departure.\r\n', 'Maria Gillespie, Kristy Tully - Saliendo - 2006', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '682-revision', '', '', '2011-01-12 21:02:17', '2011-01-12 21:02:17', '', 682, 'http://184.106.93.224/?p=1051', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
