(1343, 1, '2011-01-18 14:09:17', '2011-01-18 14:09:17', 'Jenny Holzer discusses the process behind her ongoing series of "Xenon Projections" as part of the exhibition "PROTECT PROTECT" at the Museum of Contemporary Art, Chicago. Featured works include "Projection for Chicago" (2008), a multi-part projection of the texts of Polish poet Wislawa Szymborska on building facades around the city, including the Lyric Opera House &amp; Riverside Plaza, among others. Holzer''s traveling exhibition opens at the Whitney Museum of American Art, New York on March 12, 2009.\r\n', 'Jenny Holzer - Projection For Chicago - 2009', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1312-revision', '', '', '2011-01-18 14:09:17', '2011-01-18 14:09:17', '', 1312, 'http://184.106.93.224/1312-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
