(1517, 0, '2011-01-25 03:03:29', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Cinematic trailer for novel and screenplay, "The house on Black Lake". A world-weary American woman''s vow at St. Joseph''s Oratory in Montreal leads her on a journey of self discovery and transformation in the French Canadian underground. The romantic, sexy, and dangerous contemorary gothic suspense explores how the only hope of redemption lies in the unknown.', 'Anastasia Blackwell - The House On Black Lake - 2010', '', 'pending', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2011-01-25 03:03:29', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0, 'http://rawwar.org/?p=1517', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1518, 0, '2011-01-25 03:13:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Seductive scene from novel "The House on Black Lake", www.houseonblacklake.com. Music video Features Anastasia Blackwell and Tosh Yanez. Rare Gibson Chet Atkins CE guitar solo by Peter Busboom. "The House on Black Lake" is an intoxicating journey into the underworld of Montreal that chronicles how a woman''s vow at a shrine leads her on a journey of self discovery. Stills were shot during filming of book trailer at Chateau Tivoli in San Francisco. ', 'Anastasia Blackwell - Mysterious Encounter - 2010', '', 'pending', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2011-01-25 03:13:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0, 'http://rawwar.org/?p=1518', 0, 'post', '', 0);
